properties.areaDesc: Cuyama Valley; San Luis Obispo County Mountains; San Luis Obispo County Interior Valleys
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 16 at 2:57AM PST until January 16 at 10:00PM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...South to southwest winds 20 to 35 mph with gusts up to
50 mph expected. Strongest winds expected across higher
terrain and the Carrizo Plain.

* WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Interior Valleys, Cuyama Valley
and San Luis Obispo County Mountains.

* WHEN...From 7 AM to 10 PM PST today.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Travel may become hazardous for high
profile vehicles traveling along Highways 58 and 166.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 7 AM THIS MORNING TO 10 PM PST THIS EVENING
